snippet.textDisplay: This looks like the type of movie specifically designed to win an award. Don't get me wrong,  I love Pixar but this movie looks like the most stereotypical "Family comes first adventure movie" the only difference being the fact it's Pixar making it. It doesn't feel like an original take on Hero's Journey like Up or Inside Out. It's just bland. It hypes you up for a fantastical fantasy land adventure, only to meet you with meta jokes about cellphones and "modern life"
